Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The driver sure is taking his time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what the heck's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we should go check on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:01:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Unexpected Enemy"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like no one's used this place for years...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not using the toilet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any money! So get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Switch with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these guys henchmen of Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Run towards the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in serious trouble here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take this chance and get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harpy... Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly was that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mai. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Musketeers of Doma... Amelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was another victim of Gozaburo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My little brother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...killed by your company!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, you don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took on Gozaburo's sins along with control of Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem I must solve on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They most likely have already gotten to Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what is their purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What {\b0}is{\b1} this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I supposed to pull it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your name is Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When was this card placed in my deck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this some kind of magic trick...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some kind of tremendous power guiding me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this the new path I'm supposed to follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have mail from the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please come back immediately..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going right to Industrial Illusions from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may find more information about them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't take orders from anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll decide my path myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll defeat anyone who\N dares to stand in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you keep driving straight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, our ride is ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were spacing out, we almost got caught in the explosion at the gas station!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sayin' it's {\i1}my{\i0} fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight, you jerk!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to be fighting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be thinking about what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, all we can do is go to Industrial Illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The limousine Pegasus sent for us got taken over by those other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is how we get there from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tight~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! Your suitcase is in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're talking about?! {\i1}Yours{\i0} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what the hell did you bring in that suitcase?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some {\i1}very{\i0} important stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you take a small peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cultural characteristic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach Americans about Japanese culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You twit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see this crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the {\i1}flipping hell{\i0} is {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are American boxers right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GIVE IT NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fighting at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jounouchi, was the person who saved us really Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had the Harpy Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt. She's Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she took out those Doma punks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that must mean Mai's\N fighting against them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she's here, I feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! She's so cool, that Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's the case, why didn't she tell us it was her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did we do ta' deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear your damn complain--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wallet's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd ya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-shit... WAIT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WAIT~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WAIT~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it. It's yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you two are close friends with Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we'll really meet in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, YEAH! We're his {\i1}best{\i0} friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, let {\i1}me{\i0} do all the talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what you told me,\N it seems Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s God Cards were stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows Yugi won the God Cards in the Battle City Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a ton of people after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the {\i1}ultimate{\i0} rare cards, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we, as his {\i1}closest{\i0} friends in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came to America to help him get the God Cards back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were thinking maybe we'd understand more if we paid Pegasus a little visit at his headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been troubled because I haven't been able to get a hold of Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Industrial Illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Industrial Illusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is today a holiday or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why would the doors be left wide open?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fishy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful, Other Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sensed someone with a murderous\N intent when I came in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. The phone lines are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what the?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, it's not opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, that was a pretty extreme entrance there, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, did Pegasus call you here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus is no longer here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are... Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are... you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus... I'll be taking that soul of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Magic Card, Harpy Lady Phoenix Formation, activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This card destroys Monsters on the opponent's side of the field equal to the amount of Harpy Ladies on my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}N-NOOO~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, the Attack Power of the destroyed Monster is taken as damage from the opponent's Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NOOOOOOOOOOOO~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've... {\i1}disposed{\i0} of Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! There's no way Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, Mai Kujaku said she wanted to take care of you groupies with her own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were only supposed to go after Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh and Jounouchi are {\i1}our{\i0} opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} be taking these two on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you two better keep your hands off them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a lot of fun\N hanging around you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So much so that I lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess your friendship was\N a little too bright for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you?! What the hell is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a lot of explaining to do!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Are you betraying us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} wouldn't do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Doma blackmailed you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys want to leave this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll have to defeat me in a Duel {\i1}first{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! I'll start with {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the Mai Kujaku you once knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been {\i1}reborn{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By obtaining {\i1}new{\i0} strength! The power of the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Magic Card, dyed in the darkest black! Awaken thy soul of darkness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Field Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can leave that barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the winner of the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} and Jounouchi have to Duel each other like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Harpy Lady!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gain the power of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the boundaries of the Orichalcos, all of my Monsters become Dark Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their Attack Powers go up by 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Jounouchi... it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I DON'T WANT TO FIGHT YOU LIKE THIS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:22:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the one waiting for us at Industrial Illusions was Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then after she captured Pegasus' soul with The Barrier of Orichalcos, she demanded to Duel Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too strange for you two to fight\Nunder this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with you, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you really become our enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Mai is Falling Into the Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
